"Assertive INFPs are pretty rare compared to turbulent INFPs. Here are some of their distinctive features. They're less scared of failing than the turbulent INFPs which gives them the courage to complete their tasks. Assertive INFPs tend to stand up for themselves when they need to without apologies. They state their argument when they need to rather than hold back constantly to avoid trouble. They don't run away from their problems but face them squarely."
